latestPosts.caption:
Taking college public speaking in high school definitely was worth it lol. I’m blessed to have the opportunity to use my voice to speak to the youth on topics I care deeply about such as mental health and ambition. 

I was able to do 3 presentations from pre-k to 8th grade and had a great time.

At the end of the day most people go after the things they THINK they deserve and not always what they dream about. Having good mental health impacts how children(and adults)view themselves and the world around them ensuring they keep going after their dreams.
